text:
Producer-san,
May i have a moment of your time...?
Well, it's not really a big deal.

It's okay.
I'm happy to talk to you about anything.

During this training camp,
I'll basically be here for everyone.

So, anytime you need anything...
I'll respond with the utmost priority.

Yeah.
So... what do you want to talk about?

Ah, right...
I had a dance lesson today...

I'm really curious about something, so I'd
love to get some advice from Producer-san...

I don't really know much about it either, so i
don't think i could give a proper advice on that...

No...
I just wanted to ask if you noticed anything...
